===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ML.}} {{term|homogeneus|lang=la}} < {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ὁμογενής||of the same race, family or kind|lang=grc}} <  {{term|ὁμός||same|tr=homos|lang=grc}} + {{term|γένος|tr=genos||kind|lang=grc}}. Compare {{term|homo-||same|lang=en}} and {{term|-ous|lang=en}}, adjectival suffix.

